Package ohos.ivihardware.vehiclecontrol

Class VehicleZone

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.ivihardware.vehiclecontrol.VehicleZone

  • public final class VehicleZone
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides vehicle zone information.

    The vehicle zone can be the front, rear, left, right, middle, or combined zone, such as the left front zone. In addition, this class defines the first and second rows in a particular vehicle model.

    Since:
    1
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Ivi.VehicleControl
